{"arkId":"cl010117854","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010117854","modified ":"2026-03-11","title":"Commode \u00e0 gradin, \u00e0 quatre rangs de tiroirs","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Commode \u00e0 gradin, \u00e0 quatre rangs de tiroirs\r\n"}],"displayDateCreated":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : vers 1795 - 1800","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 557 - Jacob Fr\u00e8res, Hors vitrine","room":"Salle 557, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1795,"endYear":1800,"imprecision":"vers","text":"Fin du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 5344","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"mobilier ; commode","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Grande commode rectangulaire en bois d\u0027acajou ronceux, ouvrant \u00e0 quatre tiroirs orn\u00e9s chacun d\u0027une entr\u00e9e de clef et de deux poign\u00e9es en bronze dor\u00e9 et cisel\u00e9.\r\nLes entr\u00e9es de clef se composent d\u0027une palmette et de deux t\u00eates de chiens adoss\u00e9es que surmonte une petite plaque losang\u00e9e en porcelain de Wedgwood \u00e0 buste d\u0027homme ; les poign\u00e9es, d\u0027un mascaron, de feuilles et de rubans encadrant une plaque rectangulaire de porcelaine de Wedgwood \u00e0 personnages.\r\nAux angles de la commode, une colonne saillante en bois d\u0027\u00e9b\u00e8ne \u00e0 cannelures de cuivre dor\u00e9 ; sur le dessus de marbre blanc vein\u00e9 \u00e0 quart-de-rond cisel\u00e9 en bronze dor\u00e9, un gradin \u00e0 trois panneaux d\u0027acajou encadr\u00e9s de pampres et de palmettes en bronze, orn\u00e9s de m\u00e9daillons circulaires en Wedgwood.\r\nAux extr\u00e9mit\u00e9s du gradin, un aigle en relief de bronze cisel\u00e9 et dor\u00e9.\r\nSoubassement \u00e0 frise d\u0027\u00e9toiles et de rosaces altern\u00e9es, en bronze dor\u00e9.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; 141 - 891 (?) - 37976 (au pochoir noir)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"114","displayDimension":"114 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"144","displayDimension":"144 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"61","displayDimension":"61 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau\/Technique : b\u00e2ti de ch\u00eane, placage d\u0027acajou et d\u0027\u00e9b\u00e8ne, bronze dor\u00e9, porcelaine Wedgwood, marbre blanc\r\nMat\u00e9riau : acajou\r\nMat\u00e9riau : bronze (dor\u00e9)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : marbre (blanc vein\u00e9)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : porcelaine (Wedgwood)","placeOfCreation":"France (Europe)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Achet\u00e9e d\u0027occasion au tapissier Requier en 1805 pour la chambre de Madame M\u00e8re au Grand Trianon \u00e0 Versailles ; envoy\u00e9e au ch\u00e2teau de Malmaison sous le Second Empire ; meubles et objets d\u0027art du Garde-Meuble attribu\u00e9s au Louvre par d\u00e9cret du 24 f\u00e9vrier 1901","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mobilier national (ancien Garde Meuble)","note":"","role":""}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"versement","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"24\/02\/1901","startYear":1901,"endYear":1901}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"versement"}],"place":[